Module fi.tuni.roadwatch
Package fi.tuni.roadwatch

Class SessionData

java.lang.Object
fi.tuni.roadwatch.SessionData
public class SessionData extends Object
Class containing calculation functions for the program. SessionData is also used to store data that is used in the controllers.
